title: The Pinball Arcade v1.27.7 PATCH
description:
1 - Go to your game folder and open the folder RESOURCE
2 - Copy and paste the files TCentaur.rez, TCueBallWizard.rez,TLightsCameraAction.rez and TTeedOff.rez to your RESOURCE folder.
3 - Now open the folder TABLES on your game folder, and replace the 5 enums files here to it.
4 - Now, just copy and paste the files without the folder RESOURCE HERE, to your game folder.
6 - Enjoy!
